      "comment_id" : 94570146,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Either way, these types of Answers exhibit that it&#39;s particularly the <i>enhanced</i>-for-loop that will throw <code>ConcurrentModificationException</code> - <i>not</i> the <i>traditional</i>-for-loop (although as mentioned, extra care must be taken with its incrementing)."
