      "body" : "Though short and clean, if performance/memory usage are an issue, it is worth to note that this solution runs in O(n&#178;) and creates a copy of the original list, which requires memory and an operation depending on the type of the list. Using an iterator over a LinkedList you can bring complexity down to O(n)."
